data.description: Welcome to your Mountain Retreat in the heart of Sautee Nacoochee, Georgia! This stunning Cape Cod-style home offers breathtaking mountain views with the perfect blend of rustic charm and modern elegance. With 4 bedrooms and 4 full bathrooms, including a full finished basement apartment complete with a kitchen, living room, bedroom and full bathroom, this property is a true gem for multigenerational living or potential long term rental. Step inside and be greeted by the warmth of a wood-burning fireplace, creating a cozy ambiance that's perfect for both intimate gatherings and quiet evenings. The open-concept layout flows seamlessly into the ample sized kitchen, where culinary delights await. Imagine preparing meals surrounded by the beauty of nature through large windows that frame the picturesque mountain views. With nearly 4 acres of pristine land, the possibilities are endless. From serene walks through your own private forest to hosting outdoor gatherings against the backdrop of the majestic mountains, this property offers a unique canvas for your dreams to come to life. Embrace the allure of Sautee Nacoochee, where art, culture, and the great outdoors converge. Hike through scenic trails, explore charming local shops, and savor the tranquility that only the North Georgia mountains can provide.
